Comics Reader is an old project to improve reading of Comics. Before I started using RSS readers, I used it to avoid having to browse the web pages of all my web comics I liked to read, and rather have them all on one page. Later, when I started using RSS readers, I noticed that many web comics have no RSS feed or supply only a link to the webpage. Therefore I extended this Comics Reader to provide a RSS feed of its available comics. moreâ€¦

Hope you find this useful and start to contribute yourself!

1. Copy conf.php-dist to conf.php and change to your liking.
2. Create a mysql database using the script init.sql:
   # mysql -uUSER -p DB < init.sql

